phrases: In this video, I try walking in on three of my classmates in a relationship.
I thought about messing with them, but...
They found out I am secretly a MeTuber!
I am going to have to become this weirdo's girlfriend now!
I will be your girlfriend, too!

Wh-What are you trying to do?
Maybe, now that her identity's out,
she wants a man to protect her from creepy stalkers and stuff.
Why would I ever ask anyone for help?
I j-just felt like it is time I had a boyfriend.

My long lashes and clear eyes...
You will not come across many girls as pretty as me.
I think you are really cute.
I have actually seen your videos and thought you are attractive.
It would be like a dream if I could make you my girlfriend.
Y-You are going to reject me?!
Are you actually going to reject me?
If you are just looking for a boyfriend, you will find one in no time.
But I am so cute, and I am huge on MeTube.
I am obviously better than those two!
Is that really how you choose who to date?
You are already dating two girls!
There would be no end to it if I dated everyone who is cute.
I want you to understand that, more than anything,
I want to make my two girlfriends happy.
You would have to be an idiot to reject me!
Naoya already has enough girlfriends in the two of us.
I work on my waist to maintain my figure, too!
You might get a chance to squeeze these G cups if you go out with me.
Y-You can try them out right now.

I would rather squeeze the boobs of a girl I like!
I-I cannot believe I have been defeated by the likes of him.
What should we have for dinner?
I will live with you, too.
I will let you shoot me down today.
But I am going to live with you and make you see what makes me so good.
And for power and heating and Internet.
That is good enough for you, is not it?
I do not condone a man and woman living under the same roof if they are not in a relationship.
How are you so proper when you are a two-timer?!

If I cannot live under the same roof, I will live in the yard.
Is this really the time to be impressed?!
But how did you know where we live?
I cannot wait for Nagisa-chan's dinner.
I will make you regret humiliating me.
I am going to make you fall for me!
Setting up the tent was hard...
I am camping out here until you fall in love with me.
Living in a tent sounds tough, though.
I do not think she is going to last.
They did say it is going to be chilly tonight.
Stop putting yourself in danger and go home.
I-I told you, I am not going home until you fall for me!
Are you going to live out there forever?
I care about my two girlfriends.
Everyone is making fun of me.
I just need to buy an expensive sleeping bag to bear the cold!
And I can just kill all the bugs!
I will stock up on everything I need!
Now I just need to hang on until it arrives!
And to make sure I do not run out of money...
I will shoot videos to keep it coming in!
Today, I am going to survive out in the cold in nothing but a T-shirt.
Why are you so lightly dressed, then?
It is the cleavage that earns the clicks!

I will show you what I am made of!
I can overcome the cold with exercise.
My chest's right in the shot.
She is actually going to stay until morning.
She is got a lot of stamina.
It gets cold as soon as I stop!
I-I cannot keep this up all night!
I am not falling for her.
I have nothing to fear now.
You should go home and take a shower.
Fill a black bag with water...
Throw it in a bag lined with tin foil...
And leave it in the sun.
Tighten the ropes, hang it up...
She is actually going to live here.
What a pain this has turned into.
She is cute, she is got a good figure, and she is really aggressive.
Do you really want her evil boobs to take Naoya away from us?
Unless I do something about the problem with Milika-san...
Going out with Saki-chan and Minase-san,
and making them both happy, is not going to be easy.
I need to really think about it more.
We decided we have to do something.
We need to hang in there for our goal!
Sorry, I might not have been feeling the same way.
Why are you in your swimsuits?
Because if we make you happy and get closer to you,
it will not matter anymore if Milika messes with you.
I will be your third girlfriend.
I am going to make you fall for me!

I would be glad if you appreciated that.
Naoya's going to be obsessed with me now.

Should not we be thinking about how to deal with Milika-san?!

Saki-san said we could seduce you in our swimsuits.
I did think it was a bit too blatant, but...
I think it is important to spend lots of time with you and make you like us more.
I want to do that, too.
So I put on my swimsuit, even though I was embarrassed.
I finally got to go out with Naoya-kun.
I wanted to make it last as long as I could.
It is true that we cannot let our guard down when it comes to Milika-san.
I know there is a lot more that we need to consider.
But please look at us lots, too.
There is a lot to do, but that was the most important thing.
I will look at you lots.
I am going to make you fall for me, Naoya.
Why did she have her swimsuit?
Camping videos are popular, so the outside is not bad.
I watch animeI mean, movies and stuff.
